{"tid":1738091,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"以前所有人行動之前，唔該諗埋撤退計劃","createTime":"2019-11-19T06:39:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-19T06:43:57.000Z","uid":156121,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"45f9f2e2356e10d3b1084eab4795c2f5b40eec90","tid":1738091,"uid":156121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T06:39:24.000Z","msg":"打仗最緊要係咩？係攻擊戰術？係兵力？<br />\n係撤退同補給，所謂既Exit strategy 先係最重要<br />\n<br />\n以前所有人行動之前唔該讀熟地圖<br />\n睇清楚由邊度去邊度 點去先係安全<br />\n要有心理準備要係安全地方留夜<br />\n唔好依賴家長車<br />\n<br />\n高階版就係入場之後 點樣斷後路<br />\n例如 <br />\n前排火魔法師一定要留一個後備魔法<br />\n等D狗/曱甴上前既時候近距離攻擊先有機會走同dps<br />\n大Boss鈍武都係咁死 大家要學兄弟點做<br />\n<br />\n利申: 講緊香城online"},{"pid":"53fd105c4a5afa163b1a45026c3710df16bbfca2","tid":1738091,"uid":156121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T06:39:43.000Z","msg":"推一"},{"pid":"96f6a80927fa3fc35ebf65c38df7e598ee556efd","tid":1738091,"uid":156121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T06:39:53.000Z","msg":"推二"},{"pid":"6f541cc2d2c05465e386b1c8cd2daec3a088dcdb","tid":1738091,"uid":156121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T06:40:16.000Z","msg":"推三"},{"pid":"a9011162e94207403c58d3ac14131e64b5a8ec68","tid":1738091,"uid":156121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T06:40:40.000Z","msg":"推四"},{"pid":"a26b7e510b83c3ac84b80bbbdf04bb2b414def76","tid":1738091,"uid":156121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T06:40:50.000Z","msg":"推五"},{"pid":"c10d0e8434a04703b0471a5169d5bede9b9e9116","tid":1738091,"uid":156121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T06:41:02.000Z","msg":"推六"},{"pid":"9fa89bd29ea94122cc1f23b4a09f12152b4d597e","tid":1738091,"uid":156121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T06:41:13.000Z","msg":"推七"},{"pid":"c8725d368de46e800d3b382882dd8548a35cb196","tid":1738091,"uid":156121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"repl